604
00:44:02,139 --> 00:44:05,184
Do you think a prison sentence
is really the best for someone like her?

605
00:44:06,894 --> 00:44:08,687
That's the role of the court.

606
00:44:10,189 --> 00:44:11,523
Even though we're judges,

607
00:44:12,691 --> 00:44:14,693
we can't change who she is inside.

608
00:44:15,194 --> 00:44:16,278
I'm just worried.

609
00:44:17,279 --> 00:44:19,907
She'll serve out her sentence
and grow into an adult.

610
00:44:21,617 --> 00:44:22,826
What happens after that?

611
00:44:23,494 --> 00:44:24,995
That's up to her parents.

612
00:44:26,997 --> 00:44:30,000
If only they could make her realize
how serious her crime is.

613
00:44:31,794 --> 00:44:33,003
But…

614
00:44:34,380 --> 00:44:37,007
